reviewText:
I enjoyed this DVD

Trevor B
Great gospel music by Marty and the Superlatves!
The sound and photo was great.  Thank you.
marty is the consummate enteraner. wonderful music. great songs. would recommend to all. thank you very much
Absolutely wonderful DVD. If u love Marty Stuart,Connie Smith & the Superlatives you will not be disappointed. This is so enjoyable & so much fun.  Order it now. You're going to love it!!!!!

I love Marty Stuart and the Fabulous Superlative Band is hot. Great music and songs and great voices. Plus they always come through singing Christian music. They believe in what they sing. If you love Marty buy this.

Nobody does "old style" country like Marty Stuart and he applies the same principles and power into his gospel writing and singing.  Back by the  "Fabulous Superlatives" (this is his Signature Group) and hosted by Bill Gaither, you will have a wonderful time listening to great music and hearing the stories and meaning of what you are hearing.  "The Unseen Hand" is worth the price of the DVD!
My mom has dementia and having music such as this helps to give her some peace and my dad (her caretaker) some well deserved rest.
We have watched this at least 10 times and will watch more. It is just a great video with personal time with Marty and Connie.
